                28. A axis mode

    **This mode has three options.When we use rotary angle mark,we select A mode,when we use rotary axis mark or rotary text mark ,we select X(rotary direction is in X) or Y(rotary direction is in Y) mode.**

                29. Disable A axis

    **Disable to use A axis, normally when use XZA or YZA, for special layer you can disable A axis to only move X or Y**

